WITH package_cte AS (
            SELECT id
            FROM debian_repository_package
            WHERE
                tenant_id = $1
                AND sha256sum = $2
            LIMIT 1
        )
        INSERT INTO debian_repository_component_package (
            component_id,
            package_id,
            filename,
            created_at,
            updated_at
        )
        SELECT
            $3,
            package_cte.id,
            $4,
            NOW(),
            NOW()
        FROM package_cte
        ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
